headshotImage.caption: Shahid Afridi headshot
headshotImage.longCaption: Shahid Afridi headshot

dismissalComment.html: bowled'm! Powell strikes early - Peach of a leg-cutter. Pitched on an around the middle stump and shaping away, Afridi plays all over it and the ball crashes into the woodwork. Looking to play across the line to a ball that was shaping away. Crowd goes mute and Afridi walks back counting the grass.

headshotImage.caption: Imran Farhat player page headshot cutout, 2021
headshotImage.longCaption: Imran Farhat player page headshot cutout, 2021

dismissalComment.html: gone! short and wide outside the off stump - 'the sucker ball' as the call it in Australia. Farhat goes for the cut and fails to keep it down, Gayle at gully times his jump to perfection and takes it high over his head. Only Gayle could have taken that as it was hit pretty high

headshotImage.caption: Faisal Iqbal player page headshot cutout, 2021
headshotImage.longCaption: Faisal Iqbal player page headshot cutout, 2021

dismissalComment.html: Gotcha! Banged in short and Iqbal pulled but found the man at long leg. Mohammed judged it perfectly, his feet were dangerously close to the ropes but he balanced himself, and took the catch. Pretty good innings from Iqbal comes to an end

dismissalComment.html: that's the end of that! Rana on a roll here - good length delivery on the stumps, this one straightened after hitting the deck - Simmons was done in by the extra pace and the angle. Easy decision for the umpire as Simmons was caught plumb in front. Naved-ul-Hasan is on a hat-trick here.

commentTextItems.html: And that's it. West Indies have won their first game on this tour. Full, angled across, Lara leans forward, head over the ball, square-drives it past point.

commentPostTextItems.html: It has been three and half years since Samuels went past fifty, leave alone 100. And what a nice comeback into the big league. It was a dazzling knock, full of pleasing drives, imperious lofted shots, and dismissive pulls. But the win is not all about Samuels, much of the credit should go to the bowlers who had done the hard work earlier and restricted Pakistan to a below-par total. And then Samuels decided to impose himself.

commentTextItems.html: And that great shot is followed up with a ugly swipe! Banged in short and Lara tries to slap it across but doesn't connect
Orgasmic drive over cover! What a shot! It was a length delivery but Lara leant forward, and just drove on the up. Elegant, Imperious and Languid.
That's his hundred, his second. Brought up in style.  Full and on the legs, clipped away powerfully. This has been such a dazzling knock.   Has Samuels finally arrived?

commentPreTextItems.html: And some in the crowd have had enough. they are walking out.

commentTextItems.html: Banged in short, stands up on his toes, swivels and bang, To the deep midwicket boundary
full in length, outside off, eased past cover
Ah....Length-delivery, lands on middle, came back in but Samuels adjust to that movement, whips it past midwicket
beaten. Ambitious heave outside the offstump. doesn't make contact . Lara goes across, has a chat with the youngster. Lets see what he does next ball
fullish, on the off and middle, Lara leans forward, slightly late, brings his bat down across the line, dabs the ball to midwicket

commentTextItems.html: length-delivery, outside off, Lara goes back and across, steers it to Hafeez at point
full, outside off, Lara leans forward, opens the bat-face, steers it to right of point and Hafeez makes a good diving stop

Lovely comeback from Anjum. Slower deliv ery, on the stumps,  almost had Samuels who somehow adjusted at the last minute, stopped his intended lofted drive, and pushed the delivery away to the off side

Wah! Wah! Samuels is flowing like a river tonight. Imperious lofted drive. Full in length and Samuels just took out the left foot out of the line and creamed it, in the air , between the bowler and mid-on
full-length, Lara goes back rather than forward, stabs it away to the offside
